    <p>At the bottom of each pit a deep layer of <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="生石灰"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">quicklime</code></b> steamed and seethed. <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="On the lips of the pit - (这里的lips是边缘的意思)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(坑边)</code></b> a low ridge of quicklime threw up bubbles that burst in the air above it.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Thus, in this respect, the authorities still gave thought to propriety and it was only later that, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="by the force of things"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(为形势所迫)</code></b>, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="this last remnant of decorum"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(这最后一点廉耻)</code></b> <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="went by the board (fall past the board; board - side of the ship) 出局"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________([行为方式]被放弃)</code></b>, and men and women were flung into the death-pits indiscriminately.</p>
