  <li>
    <p>In the period we are now concerned with, the separation of the sexes was still in force and the authorities <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="set great store by it"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(认为它极为必要)</code></b>.</p>
