    <p>But, paradoxically enough, once the whole town was in the grip of the disease, its very prevalence tended to make things easier, since the disorganization of the town’s economic life <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="threw a great number of persons out of work"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(造成了大量人员失业)</code></b>.</p>
